data.description: Absolutely adorable 4 bedroom, 2 bath South Lyon home within walking distance to downtown and South Lyon High School. This home features a recently updated Kitchen (2023)  with all new appliances, white cabinets & granite cabinets.   The large center island w/ breakfast bar seating makes entertaining while cooking a breeze. Luxury Vinyl flooring throughout most all of the main level. Three bedrooms and full Bath on the main floor (one bedroom can flex as Dining Room or office  w/ a closet & French doors that open to the Living Room). Expansive Family room off the back of the home with eat-in dining area, opens to the covered backyard patio. This charming space  is the perfect area to enjoy warm summer nights sipping tea & enjoying a good book. Upstairs is the spacious Owners Suite with ge Upstairs is the spacious Owners Suite with generous walk-in closet & full bathroom. Unfshd Basemnt ready for finishing touches offers laundry & plenty of room for Movie Nights. New hot water heater in 2023. Roof and Hvac system 15 yrs old. Newer garage floor & driveway. Spacious rolling backyard with lovely perennials.
